{
  "video_id": "2wu28tI9VkM",
  "title": "What we're missing in the debate about immigration | Duarte Geraldino",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13166.0,
      "end_time": 15439.0,
      "text": "So, Ma was trying to explain something to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15463.0,
      "end_time": 17253.0,
      "text": "about Grandma and when they grew up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17278.0,
      "end_time": 18985.0,
      "text": "but I couldn&#39;t pay attention to her"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19900.0,
      "end_time": 21941.0,
      "text": "because I was five years old, and I was petrified."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21965.0,
      "end_time": 24950.0,
      "text": "I had just seen The Green Lady."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24974.0,
      "end_time": 27973.0,
      "text": "Now, about a week earlier, I&#39;d watched that movie \"Godzilla,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27997.0,
      "end_time": 31144.0,
      "text": "the one about that huge lizard-like beast storming a major city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31168.0,
      "end_time": 35485.0,
      "text": "and the thought of a green monster coming for me was stuck in my mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35850.0,
      "end_time": 39139.0,
      "text": "And yet there I was, at the tip of Lower Manhattan with my mom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39163.0,
      "end_time": 40943.0,
      "text": "just staring at her:"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40968.0,
      "end_time": 42127.0,
      "text": "her horns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42151.0,
      "end_time": 43312.0,
      "text": "her muscles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43336.0,
      "end_time": 44717.0,
      "text": "all of it just frightened me."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44741.0,
      "end_time": 49114.0,
      "text": "And I didn&#39;t know whether she was a monster or a hero."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49138.0,
      "end_time": 52360.0,
      "text": "So I decided to consult the Google of the day --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52384.0,
      "end_time": 53664.0,
      "text": "\"Ma! Ma!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53688.0,
      "end_time": 55584.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55608.0,
      "end_time": 60490.0,
      "text": "My mother explained that The Green Lady is actually the Statue of Liberty"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60730.0,
      "end_time": 62344.0,
      "text": "and that she was waving immigrants in."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62368.0,
      "end_time": 66663.0,
      "text": "Now, the part of her explanation that really messed with my young head"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66687.0,
      "end_time": 69322.0,
      "text": "was the fact that, according to Ma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69346.0,
      "end_time": 71379.0,
      "text": "long before us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71403.0,
      "end_time": 74555.0,
      "text": "The Green Lady was actually brown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75202.0,
      "end_time": 76554.0,
      "text": "brown like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76579.0,
      "end_time": 79440.0,
      "text": "and that she changed colors over the years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79904.0,
      "end_time": 81238.0,
      "text": "much like America."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81262.0,
      "end_time": 86556.0,
      "text": "Now, the part that really is intriguing about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86580.0,
      "end_time": 88211.0,
      "text": "is that when she changed colors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88235.0,
      "end_time": 89976.0,
      "text": "she made me think about myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90481.0,
      "end_time": 91875.0,
      "text": "It all made sense to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91900.0,
      "end_time": 93897.0,
      "text": "because as a first-generation American,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93921.0,
      "end_time": 95398.0,
      "text": "I was surrounded by immigrants."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95422.0,
      "end_time": 99232.0,
      "text": "In fact, within my immediate social circle of the people who support me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99256.0,
      "end_time": 100544.0,
      "text": "who enrich my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100568.0,
      "end_time": 102455.0,
      "text": "at least two are foreign-born."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103199.0,
      "end_time": 106851.0,
      "text": "My life as a US citizen is in many ways shaped by newcomers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 106875.0,
      "end_time": 108340.0,
      "text": "and chances are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108580.0,
      "end_time": 109510.0,
      "text": "so is yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109534.0,
      "end_time": 113187.0,
      "text": "There are more than 40 million immigrants in the USA."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113211.0,
      "end_time": 114721.0,
      "text": "According to census data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 114745.0,
      "end_time": 119407.0,
      "text": "a quarter of the nation&#39;s children have at least one foreign-born parent."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119431.0,
      "end_time": 124542.0,
      "text": "I know all these statistics because I study global migration patterns."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124566.0,
      "end_time": 126728.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a journalist, and for the last few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126752.0,
      "end_time": 129158.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been documenting the lives of US citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 129183.0,
      "end_time": 131111.0,
      "text": "who&#39;ve lost people to deportation."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 131135.0,
      "end_time": 133438.0,
      "text": "And the numbers are enormous."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 134360.0,
      "end_time": 136584.0,
      "text": "From 2008 to 2016,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136608.0,
      "end_time": 139902.0,
      "text": "more than three million people were \"ordered removed\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139926.0,
      "end_time": 142952.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the technical term for being deported."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 143415.0,
      "end_time": 148932.0,
      "text": "There is an economic, a political, a psychological and an emotional cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 148956.0,
      "end_time": 150851.0,
      "text": "to those deportations --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150876.0,
      "end_time": 153678.0,
      "text": "the moments when these circles are broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 153702.0,
      "end_time": 155448.0,
      "text": "I once asked a US soldier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 155472.0,
      "end_time": 157807.0,
      "text": "\"Why did you volunteer to fight this war?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 157831.0,
      "end_time": 159100.0,
      "text": "And she told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159340.0,
      "end_time": 161190.0,
      "text": "\"Because I&#39;m proud to defend my country.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 161440.0,
      "end_time": 162210.0,
      "text": "But I pressed to know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 162234.0,
      "end_time": 164910.0,
      "text": "\"Really, when you&#39;re on base,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 164115.0,
      "end_time": 166354.0,
      "text": "and you hear bombs exploding in the distance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 166378.0,
      "end_time": 170154.0,
      "text": "and you see soldiers coming back who are gravely injured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 170179.0,
      "end_time": 174338.0,
      "text": "in that moment, when you know you could be next,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 174362.0,
      "end_time": 175993.0,
      "text": "what does &#39;my country&#39; mean?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176806.0,
      "end_time": 177956.0,
      "text": "She looked at me."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 178568.0,
      "end_time": 180435.0,
      "text": "\"My country is my wife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 180459.0,
      "end_time": 181773.0,
      "text": "my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 181797.0,
      "end_time": 183357.0,
      "text": "my friends, my soldiers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 183381.0,
      "end_time": 184698.0,
      "text": "What she was telling me"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 184722.0,
      "end_time": 188900.0,
      "text": "is that \"my country\" is a collection of these strong relationships;"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 188114.0,
      "end_time": 189983.0,
      "text": "these social circles."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 190406.0,
      "end_time": 192626.0,
      "text": "When the social circles are weakened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 192650.0,
      "end_time": 194682.0,
      "text": "a country itself is weaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 195255.0,
      "end_time": 198845.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re missing a crucial aspect in the debate about immigration policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 198869.0,
      "end_time": 200892.0,
      "text": "Rather than focusing on individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 200916.0,
      "end_time": 203942.0,
      "text": "we should focus on the circles around them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 203967.0,
      "end_time": 206956.0,
      "text": "because these are the people who are left behind:"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 206980.0,
      "end_time": 208859.0,
      "text": "the voters, the taxpayers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 208884.0,
      "end_time": 211161.0,
      "text": "the ones who are suffering that loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 211186.0,
      "end_time": 213468.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just the children of the deported"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 213492.0,
      "end_time": 214833.0,
      "text": "who are impacted."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 214857.0,
      "end_time": 217734.0,
      "text": "You have brothers and sisters who are separated by borders."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 217758.0,
      "end_time": 220565.0,
      "text": "You have classmates, teachers, law enforcement officers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 220589.0,
      "end_time": 222821.0,
      "text": "technologists, scientists, doctors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 222845.0,
      "end_time": 226563.0,
      "text": "who are all scrambling to make sense of new realities"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 226587.0,
      "end_time": 229180.0,
      "text": "when their social circles are broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 229885.0,
      "end_time": 233540.0,
      "text": "These are the real lives behind all these statistics"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 233564.0,
      "end_time": 236120.0,
      "text": "that dominate discussions about immigration policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 236360.0,
      "end_time": 237997.0,
      "text": "But we don&#39;t often think about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 238210.0,
      "end_time": 239534.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m trying to change that."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 239917.0,
      "end_time": 243874.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s just one of the real-life stories that I&#39;ve collected."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 244550.0,
      "end_time": 245918.0,
      "text": "And it still haunts me."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 246482.0,
      "end_time": 250227.0,
      "text": "I met Ramon and his son in 2016,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 250251.0,
      "end_time": 253787.0,
      "text": "the same year both of them were being ordered out of the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 254459.0,
      "end_time": 258349.0,
      "text": "Ramon was being deported to Latin America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 258373.0,
      "end_time": 261697.0,
      "text": "while his son, who was a sergeant in the US military,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 261721.0,
      "end_time": 263291.0,
      "text": "was being deployed."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 264596.0,
      "end_time": 265798.0,
      "text": "Deported ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 266479.0,
      "end_time": 267679.0,
      "text": "deployed."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 268308.0,
      "end_time": 271294.0,
      "text": "If you just look at Ramon&#39;s case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 271318.0,
      "end_time": 274585.0,
      "text": "it wouldn&#39;t be clear how deeply connected to the country he is."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 275307.0,
      "end_time": 276627.0,
      "text": "But consider his son:"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 277159.0,
      "end_time": 280982.0,
      "text": "a US citizen defending a country that&#39;s banished his father."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 281499.0,
      "end_time": 283382.0,
      "text": "The social circle is what&#39;s key here."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 283955.0,
      "end_time": 287383.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s another example that illustrates those critical bonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 287408.0,
      "end_time": 290746.0,
      "text": "A group of citizens in Philadelphia were concerned about their jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 290770.0,
      "end_time": 293760.0,
      "text": "because the legal owner of the restaurant where they worked"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 293785.0,
      "end_time": 295525.0,
      "text": "was an undocumented immigrant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 295549.0,
      "end_time": 297825.0,
      "text": "and immigration officials had picked him up."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 298218.0,
      "end_time": 299561.0,
      "text": "They rallied behind him."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 299585.0,
      "end_time": 301800.0,
      "text": "An immigration lawyer argued"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 301320.0,
      "end_time": 303205.0,
      "text": "he was too important to the local community"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 303230.0,
      "end_time": 304678.0,
      "text": "to be deported."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 304702.0,
      "end_time": 308760.0,
      "text": "At the hearing, they even submitted restaurant reviews --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 308784.0,
      "end_time": 310530.0,
      "text": "restaurant reviews!"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 310645.0,
      "end_time": 315313.0,
      "text": "In the end, a judge exercised what&#39;s called \"judicial discretion\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 315337.0,
      "end_time": 317272.0,
      "text": "and allowed him to stay in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 317297.0,
      "end_time": 320783.0,
      "text": "but only because they considered the social circle."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 321647.0,
      "end_time": 326409.0,
      "text": "There are 23 million noncitizens in the USA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 326434.0,
      "end_time": 328502.0,
      "text": "according to verifiable federal data."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 328526.0,
      "end_time": 330688.0,
      "text": "And that doesn&#39;t include the undocumented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 330712.0,
      "end_time": 334660.0,
      "text": "because numbers for that population are at best complex estimates."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 334900.0,
      "end_time": 336347.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s just work with what we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 336372.0,
      "end_time": 339414.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s 23 million social circles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 339438.0,
      "end_time": 342342.0,
      "text": "about 100 million individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 342367.0,
      "end_time": 345466.0,
      "text": "whose lives could be impacted by deportation."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 345490.0,
      "end_time": 348663.0,
      "text": "And the stress of it all is trickling down through the population."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 349341.0,
      "end_time": 352962.0,
      "text": "A 2017 poll by UCLA of LA County residents"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 352986.0,
      "end_time": 356759.0,
      "text": "found that 30 percent of citizens in LA County"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 356783.0,
      "end_time": 359104.0,
      "text": "are stressed about deportation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 359128.0,
      "end_time": 362104.0,
      "text": "not because they themselves could be removed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 362128.0,
      "end_time": 366869.0,
      "text": "but rather, because members of their social circle were at risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 367823.0,
      "end_time": 370518.0,
      "text": "I am not suggesting that no one should ever be deported;"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 370542.0,
      "end_time": 372393.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t confuse me with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 372417.0,
      "end_time": 376583.0,
      "text": "But what I am saying is that we need to look at the bigger picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 377692.0,
      "end_time": 380450.0,
      "text": "If you are within the sound of my voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 380690.0,
      "end_time": 382519.0,
      "text": "I want you to close your eyes for a moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 382543.0,
      "end_time": 385172.0,
      "text": "and examine your own social circle."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 385923.0,
      "end_time": 387536.0,
      "text": "Who are your foreign-born?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 388120.0,
      "end_time": 391874.0,
      "text": "What would it feel like if the circle were broken?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 392488.0,
      "end_time": 393833.0,
      "text": "Share your story."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 394550.0,
      "end_time": 397174.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m building a global archive of first-person accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 397198.0,
      "end_time": 399459.0,
      "text": "and linking them with mapping technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 399483.0,
      "end_time": 403387.0,
      "text": "so that we can see exactly where these circles break,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 403411.0,
      "end_time": 406485.0,
      "text": "because this is not just an American issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 406816.0,
      "end_time": 410370.0,
      "text": "There are a quarter-billion migrants around the world;"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 410610.0,
      "end_time": 414135.0,
      "text": "people living, loving and learning in countries where they were not born."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 414160.0,
      "end_time": 416792.0,
      "text": "And in my career, in my life, I&#39;ve been one of them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 416816.0,
      "end_time": 419798.0,
      "text": "in China, in Africa, in Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 419822.0,
      "end_time": 422972.0,
      "text": "And each time I become one of these foreigners --"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 422996.0,
      "end_time": 426149.0,
      "text": "one of these strange-looking guys in a new land --"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 426173.0,
      "end_time": 428142.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t help but think back to that day"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 428166.0,
      "end_time": 430522.0,
      "text": "when I was in Lower Manhattan with my mom"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 430546.0,
      "end_time": 432450.0,
      "text": "all those decades ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 432474.0,
      "end_time": 434720.0,
      "text": "when I was scared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 434960.0,
      "end_time": 436727.0,
      "text": "and I had just spotted that green lady."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 437624.0,
      "end_time": 441730.0,
      "text": "And I guess the question that I keep on thinking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 441754.0,
      "end_time": 443600.0,
      "text": "when I see her"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 443300.0,
      "end_time": 447289.0,
      "text": "and all the younger replicas of her that are so obviously brown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 447314.0,
      "end_time": 450127.0,
      "text": "and even the paintings that showcase her in the beginning"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 450151.0,
      "end_time": 452257.0,
      "text": "as not quite green --"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 453532.0,
      "end_time": 455239.0,
      "text": "when I look at all of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 456380.0,
      "end_time": 459386.0,
      "text": "the question that my research seeks to answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 459410.0,
      "end_time": 463707.0,
      "text": "becomes, to me, the same one that confounded me all those years ago:"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 464652.0,
      "end_time": 466920.0,
      "text": "Is she a monster"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 467110.0,
      "end_time": 468266.0,
      "text": "or a hero?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 469271.0,
      "end_time": 470421.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 470445.0,
      "end_time": 473467.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}